title: 'Orange Is The New Black' Season 5 Finally Has Release Date | Letty B | 102 The River
text:
'Orange Is The New Black' Season 5 Finally Has Release Date posted by Letty B - share 
Source: YouTube 
The show you love to binge watch on Netflix, Orange Is The New Black FINALLY has a release date! Season 5 (wait, there's already been 5 seasons - woah) is set to hit Netflix on June 9th. Perfect for the start of summer vacation. 
There was a short teaser released with the announcement today (February 8th), where we are reminded of the cliffhanger ending from season four. So mark your calendars and catch up if you need to because OITNB will be back before we know it!
